snippet.title: Green Hell VR Official Teaser - PCVR
snippet.description:
The highly anticipated teaser of Green Hell VR is finally here! Which mechanic are you the most excited to try out in virtual reality?

Join us at a Discord server dedicated to the game, where you can ask questions about the production, chat with developers, and exchange your thoughts with other fans of the game. 
The following link is the invitation code: https://discord.gg/cn7DTwuKGp.
